data.description: ACTIVE UNDER CONTRACT - ACCEPTING BACK UP OFFERS.- Welcome home to your POOL HOME at 11472 McLeod St. where you will find a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with all the charm and space you need for a comfortable Florida lifestyle. When you arrive at this home, you will immediately notice the curb appeal with the paver driveway and meticulous landscaping. You will enter the home to the formal living/dining room with laminate floors, which leads to the kitchen and family room, providing a spacious floor plan for entertaining family and friends. The kitchen features 42-inch wood cabinets, Corian counters, and stainless-steel appliances, including a newer stove, microwave, dishwasher, and sink. The kitchen overlooks the family room where you can curl up to read a book by the wood burning fireplace. When entertainment is not on your agenda, you can retreat to your master suite with two walk-in closets and sliding glass doors leading to the outdoor lanai. Or ease into a hot bath in your master bathroom garden tub. The master bathroom has a separate shower, double sinks and plenty of cabinet and counter space. This functional split floor plan features the second and third bedrooms on the opposite side of the home with the second bathroom. If the beauty of this home's interior is not enough, step outside through the sliding glass doors onto the screened lanai with a private pool! Not many homes in the community have a private pool to relax in the sun during the warmer months. All but two windows have been replaced. Shingle roof was replaced in 2023. HVAC was replaced in July 2022. Wellington at Seven Hills is a gated 55+, maintenance free community with a club house, community pool, restaurant, fitness center, and tennis courts. Spectrum Fiber Optics is currently being installed throughout the community. Perfectly located within the community with a close by resident only gate, and also close to the Suncoast Parkway. No flood insurance required.
